This directory (test_Ar_periodic_FCC_MI_OPBC_f90) contains a test that computes the
energy per atom in an infinite perfect FCC crystal of Argon using the MI-OPBC-H or
MI-OPBC-F NBC.  (The test uses the Model's cutoff to create a configuration just big
enough for use by the minimum image convention.

Makefile                             -- makefile to compile and build executables with
                                        GNU or Intel compilers
README                               -- this file 
test_Ar_periodic_FCC_MI_OPBC_f90.F90 -- Code for the test
test_Ar_periodic_FCC_MI_OPBC_f90.kim -- KIM descriptor file for the test

